{"tid":986318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全球裁員】Tesla削減7%全職員工 結束車主引薦計劃","createTime":"2019-01-18T10:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T10:42:41.000Z","uid":26418,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2453e09ce1253fc8c3abbb998e5f6d27fe9f4b28","tid":986318,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"電動車開發商特斯拉（Tesla）稱，將削減約7%全職員工，只會留下最重要的臨時工及合約人員。特斯拉稱，去年是特朗拉史上最具挑戰的一年。去年第三季，公司利潤約4%。第四季初步估算仍是有盈利的，但按通用會計準則（GAAP）計的利潤略低於第三季。該公司表示，在需要提高Model 3產量之際同時進行裁員，未來幾個月將有很多製造設施的改進，由5月起需要向所有市場交付Model 3。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年10月止，特斯拉擁有約45000名員工，按此計算，是次裁員7%將涉約3000人。<br />\n<br />\n除了裁員，特斯拉也在其他方面削減成本，將在2月起結束車主引薦計劃（referral program）。該計劃讓特斯拉的車主向親友提供個人推薦編碼，讓他們於購買新車後，享有6個月免費無限超級充電服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1547807673675&amp;issue=20190118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1547807673675%26issue%3D20190118&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7qMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=cfc30b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1547807673675%26issue%3D20190118&h=8b043a59\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1547807673675&amp;issue=20190118</a>"},{"pid":"02d1fce2e5314e0270c0a7fc651b5654061812db","tid":986318,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"Apple同阿里巴巴又話要請少啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb25ba08411fe78a27c4ef1905574e5092f0ff4","tid":986318,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"中國設廠咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}